Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.56,0:00:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}Looking up far, far away\N{\c&He1e1e1&}into the vast sea of space,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.24,0:00:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}those who are able to see the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Galaxy Railways are fortunate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}This is because they are the ones who are\N{\c&He1e1e1&}able to see hope in their own futures.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.25,0:00:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.25,0:00:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Brother, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.92,0:00:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Brother Mamoru! Why did you have to die!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.27,0:00:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Brother, I'm going, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.91,0:01:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}"Time's Knot"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.55,0:01:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu! Manabu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.22,0:01:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.56,0:01:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Just get yourself down here, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.22,0:01:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What is it, Mom? Why the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}stern look on your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.23,0:01:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.56,0:01:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What's what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What is the meaning of this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.91,0:01:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Is it a love letter, Manabu-{\i1}chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.91,0:01:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm so jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Were you planning on joining the Space\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Defense Force without telling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.92,0:01:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Your father, your brother, and now you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.59,0:01:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I absolutely will not permit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.59,0:01:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.93,0:02:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If you insist on going, then as of\N{\c&He1e1e1&}today, I will disown you as my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Now, now, don't be so upset, Kanna-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.27,0:02:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu, you should\N{\c&He1e1e1&}apologize to her at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.54,0:02:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.87,0:02:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu, you're going to work\N{\c&He1e1e1&}in the mines with us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I... plan on going into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Kanna-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.23,0:02:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}He's just like you, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.57,0:02:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}So much so that I can't bear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.25,0:03:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu, listen close to what your brother\N{\c&He1e1e1&}says, and help your mom out for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu, look after Mom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}Right, I'll take care of her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}Dad... Brother Mamoru... I'm sorry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}I just can't...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.21,0:03:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}...I can't abandon my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Just a moment, Manabu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Take this {\i1}bento{\i0} lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.19,0:04:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.86,0:04:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}The train on Track 3\N{\c&He1e1e1&}is bound for Destiny.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Congratulations on joining the force.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.21,0:04:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}From now on, we're both fellow workers\N{\c&He1e1e1&}for Galaxy Railways Corporation, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.54,0:04:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.57,0:04:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This train is headed to Planet\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Destiny via the Altair star system.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We will be stopping at stations\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Hope and Zetsubo ("Despair").
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.19,0:05:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Also, along the way, we will\N{\c&He1e1e1&}be passing by Time's Knot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.86,0:05:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}As we do, there is a risk\N{\c&He1e1e1&}of electromagnetic harm,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}so we ask that you please\N{\c&He1e1e1&}not open any windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What is Time's Knot?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's an area where time\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and space are distorted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.27,0:05:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I hear that inside there,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}things often go all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.54,0:05:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Is that supposed to be a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Louis Fort Drake. Call me Louis.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.89,0:05:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We're traveling together,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}so let's be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki Manabu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.56,0:05:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki-{\i1}kun{\i0}, huh? Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're joining the Space\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Defense Force, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:05:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Me, {\i1}too{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.23,0:06:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We're both joining at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Almost twenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You don't look it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.18,0:06:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I thought you were younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}See here, it's not polite to ask\N{\c&He1e1e1&}a lady her age right off the bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}But you're the one who\N{\c&He1e1e1&}asked first, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Two years younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.19,0:06:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Do I look older?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}People always say I look older.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Maybe it's because\N{\c&He1e1e1&}you're a smart-aleck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm surprised they accepted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I did graduate at the top of\N{\c&He1e1e1&}my class at training school!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There weren't many other students, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You disgust me, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That goes double for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We're about to approach Time's Knot.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Please close your window.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Close it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.22,0:06:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Why don't you close it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Either one of you will be fine.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Please close it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:07:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It was an accident! Who would\N{\c&He1e1e1&}ever want to hold your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.16,0:08:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The No. 550 Express is experiencing\N{\c&He1e1e1&}a slight control glitch
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.40,0:08:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}due to some engine trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}but there is no major problem.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Please do not panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yes, there {\i1}is{\i0} a major problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm going to go see the engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm coming too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Please, relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What the hell happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The train has entered Time's Knot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.86,0:08:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Receiving a rescue request from\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the {\i1}No. 550 Hakuba Express{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.53,0:08:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It appears they have had an\N{\c&He1e1e1&}accident near Time's Knot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Dispatch the Space Defense Force at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Issuing dispatch orders\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to the Sirius Platoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}System check!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}System check, standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.54,0:08:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Orbital radar shows all clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Big One{\i0} ready to depart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.21,0:08:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Ascent Float lock confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Gravitational barrier\N{\c&He1e1e1&}generator systems normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.82,0:09:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Energy normal. Pressure within the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}boiler is rising. Cylinder valves open.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.16,0:09:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Engaging main circuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.83,0:09:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Engaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.16,0:09:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Systems all green!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.17,0:09:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Big One{\i0}, move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hey, you folks, snap to!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.22,0:10:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.56,0:10:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Planet Hakumei ("Early Death").
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We're in the desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.57,0:10:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.92,0:10:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm Yuuki Mamoru, of the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Space Panzer Grenadiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.92,0:10:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I came to rescue you, after I\N{\c&He1e1e1&}saw your emergency landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.59,0:10:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Space Panzer Grenadiers?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You mean the Special Forces squadron\N{\c&He1e1e1&}of the Space Defense Force,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.60,0:10:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}organized from the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}elites among the elite?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.77,0:10:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's an honor to meet you\N{\c&He1e1e1&}in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.27,0:11:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We were just joining the force ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Something's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.55,0:11:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Damn. Those miserable vultures!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Does this train have a stealth function?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.88,0:11:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Y- yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.22,0:11:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Activating {\i1}No. 550's{\i0} optical camouflage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.23,0:11:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If we want to protect the train and its\N{\c&He1e1e1&}passengers, we'll have to become decoys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.23,0:11:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If you're joining the SDF,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}then come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.57,0:11:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.91,0:11:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Rotten Space Panzers! I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.25,0:11:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hold on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm not letting you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It looks like we'll be\N{\c&He1e1e1&}okay for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Have we fallen into a\N{\c&He1e1e1&}tear in space-time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}So it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}When is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We have time-slipped to five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Sure enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What do you mean? Tell me what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This is the world of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.58,0:12:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If we return before\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the time hole closes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}we should be able to get back\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to our original time and space.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}But how do we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There is a distress signal being\N{\c&He1e1e1&}broadcast continually from the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:13:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It should reach a rescue\N{\c&He1e1e1&}team before long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.26,0:13:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}But what will happen to Brother!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}He is my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Five years ago, he died here on\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Planet Hakumei in the line of duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.87,0:13:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}He died? That's terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}My brother is going to die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.21,0:13:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It looks to me like you're\N{\c&He1e1e1&}not kidding about this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}In this case, please follow the Galaxy\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Railways administrative manual.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.88,0:13:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manual?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.22,0:13:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Galaxy Railways Operational\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Regulations, Article 33, Item 2:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.55,0:13:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}"Those who have time-slipped\N{\c&He1e1e1&}must by no means
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}intervene with the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}events of the past."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You must not change the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}destiny of your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.23,0:13:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What's this about destiny?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.23,0:13:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Er, nothing, nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.57,0:13:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We'll get out of here in another hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.24,0:13:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You guys get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.85,0:14:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Those guys are in league with\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the space pirate Guy Sander.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.19,0:14:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}They're guys who have prices on their\N{\c&He1e1e1&}heads, who raid the area around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.19,0:14:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Where are the other squadron members?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.86,0:14:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}They're defending the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.36,0:14:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Our strategy is to simultaneously\N{\c&He1e1e1&}commence an attack on them at daybreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}They know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}They know you're going to come after them,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and they're setting a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.21,0:14:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's true, I tell you!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Everyone is going to die down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.21,0:14:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Believe me, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.55,0:14:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Again with that "brother" business, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.55,0:14:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Cut it out, would you?\N{\c&He1e1e1&}You're older than me, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.89,0:14:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I may be older than you right now,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}but five years ago, I was younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm Manabu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.23,0:14:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're kidding... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.52,0:15:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Is it really you, Manabu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.19,0:15:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You sure went and grew up big.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Is Mom doing all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.19,0:15:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}She's the same as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}She must have been against\N{\c&He1e1e1&}you joining the SDF, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.53,0:15:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'll bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Brother, run away from here with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.54,0:15:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu, obey the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.54,0:15:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Your actions here amount to\N{\c&He1e1e1&}intervention with the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.54,0:15:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}But!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.54,0:15:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm glad you feel this way.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I don't want to die, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I never intended to die\N{\c&He1e1e1&}here in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}But I am still a Space Panzer Grenadier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I can't just run away when\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the enemy is before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't worry. Something will turn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's about time we got going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.51,0:16:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It is nearly the scheduled time\N{\c&He1e1e1&}for the Sirius Platoon to arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.52,0:16:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Is that right? Captain Bulge\N{\c&He1e1e1&}is coming for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.85,0:16:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}In that case, you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.86,0:16:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}He's the one who brought us Dad's pistol.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.87,0:16:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Of all the SDF members that\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I know, he's Number One.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.54,0:16:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}An ambush!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Dart about while running\N{\c&He1e1e1&}away, will you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You guys get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.52,0:17:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Let me handle this!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Get back to where {\i1}No. 550{\i0} is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}They're here for you! Go, Manabu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Run, Louis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}One after the next, my quarry is\N{\c&He1e1e1&}increasing! Come on out, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We're almost at the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}landing point of {\i1}No. 550{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.83,0:18:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Disengaging {\i1}No. 550's{\i0} optical camouflage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hurry up and get aboard, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.51,0:18:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.51,0:18:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu! Get on that train, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Make a fool of me, will you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Open fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Quickly! Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.19,0:18:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Panzer Grenadiers, commence attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.87,0:18:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Assist the SDF in their\N{\c&He1e1e1&}rescue operations!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Copy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hook up at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain Bulge, coupling complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.49,0:19:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Get us out of here immediately\N{\c&He1e1e1&}with {\i1}No. 550{\i0} in tow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.16,0:19:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.16,0:19:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Big One{\i0}, launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu, catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.56,0:19:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Let's play it again sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.90,0:19:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Brother! Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I cannot board that train.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.24,0:19:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Destinies should be changed\N{\c&He1e1e1&}by one's own power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm going to stake everything on that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.25,0:19:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Brother! Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.60,0:19:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What are you doing!?\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Let go of me! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.60,0:20:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.28,0:20:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Damn it! It wasn't\N{\c&He1e1e1&}supposed to be like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.15,0:20:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I wasn't supposed to\N{\c&He1e1e1&}die here... Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.22,0:20:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's all right. I'm not about\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to kick the bucket here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I promised Manabu... that I\N{\c&He1e1e1&}would change my destiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu, you go on living...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yum... Mom's rice ball...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}Sometimes, fate can toy with people.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}In most cases, they do not\N{\c&He1e1e1&}realize the reasons why,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.23,0:21:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}until much time has gone by.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That is the Supreme Commander of the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Galaxy Railways Administration,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.92,0:22:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Layla Destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.59,0:22:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Her?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.92,0:22:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All hands, salute\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Supreme Commander Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.26,0:22:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You new members have enrolled\N{\c&He1e1e1&}in the Space Defense Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.20,0:22:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm counting on you all to see to it\N{\c&He1e1e1&}that the Galaxy Railways run smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.21,0:22:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}Dad... Brother...\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I've finally made it this far.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.89,0:22:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}Me? Why is she looking at me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.23,0:22:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu, I've been waiting a\N{\c&He1e1e1&}long time for you to come.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.59,0:23:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}"Next Episode Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.03,0:23:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}I have been assigned to Sirius Platoon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.40,0:23:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}But Captain Bulge and all the other\N{\c&He1e1e1&}members give me the cold shoulder.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.04,0:23:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce, why do you hate\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the very sight of me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.71,0:23:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}Tales of the Galaxy Railroad,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Episode 3: {\i0}"The Driving Wheel of Fate"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.04,0:23:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}We're going to encounter\N{\c&He1e1e1&}something at the next station.{\i0}